B) Dr.Umar in Wilmington(DE): Tuesday September 21st@5pm-10pm, “Team Panafrikan/I.M.I.P.A.P 16th Anniversary New Members Orientation(FREE)” Please email interest letter to TeamPanAfrican@Yahoo.Com (Private Location Will Be Given to Selected Applicants Only) Serious PanAfrikanists Only, No Weaves, Perms, European Hair Color (straightening combs & braids will be tolerated), No S.B. Crisis Victims, No AlphaGangMembers, 844-4DR-UMAR

C) Dr.Umar Returns to Cincinatti(OH): Sunday September 26th@3pm, “King Kong Konsciousness Party, Lecture & Booksigning” 2141 Central Avenue 45214, info@artsota.com, 844-4DR-UMAR (1st Cincinnati lecture since September 25th 2015)

D) Dr.Umar Returns to Brooklyn(NYC): Saturday October 2nd@8am-8pm(must be seated by 10am), “5 Boroughs Black Parent Know Your School Rights BootKamp” Superior Daycare Center, 1741 Broadway, 844-4DR-UMAR, DrUmarJohnson.com, https://www.eventbee.com/v/new-york-city-black-parent-know-your-school-rights-training-bootkamp/event?eid=158095583
